overview:
Ang Bilmoko.com ay para sa pinoy.

Bilmoko.com is affiliated with the largest, widest and most reputable online service providers offering our kababayans the convenience to find the products and services they need. Pinoys, here and abroad, can gain access to different sites providing specific services.

Here are the different categories included. Most, if not all services, have a worldwide coverage. You can search, compare prices and make a booking wherever you are.

* Classifieds
  Free classifieds. Sell, buy, trade, discuss, organize, and meet people near you, wherever you may reside in the world.
* Pinoy Directory
  Locate Pinoy-owned businesses in different countries. And support foreign- owned businesses in the Philippines. Register your business here so that Pinoys can locate you.
* Car Rental
  Get the best deals on Car Rentals. Available cars in many countries!
* Flight Booking
  Shop for discount travel. Book your local and international flights here!
* Hotel Booking
  Over 71,000+ hotels in 71 countries. Book them here!
* Sightseeing Tours
  Sightseeing tours, activities and things to do in more than 450 destinations worldwide, from Paris to Rome, New York to Sydney.
* Event Tickets
  Ticketing services for leading arenas, stadiums, professional sports franchises and leagues, college sports teams, performing arts venues, museums, and theaters.
* Insurance
  Get affordable health insurance quotes and compare individual health insurance plans side by side. Find individual health insurance, family medical insurance or small business health insurance and the best medical insurance plans for your needs and budget.
* Course Finder
  Search for courses in your location and add the schedule to your calendar. Coming Soon!
* Shopping
  Shop in US internet online sites and have it delivered to your door in Manila via Forex or Johnny Air Cargo. Popular Malls in the Philippines.
* Cellphone Loads
  Buy your Prepaid Loads online. Gamecards. Internet and phone cards.
* Balikbayan Box
  Door to door delivery. A household name of every Filipino in the US.
* Flowers
  Delivers flowers around the world for all occassions.
